    }
}

{
    "command": {
        "name": "memory_add",
        "args":{
            "key": "statue_of_hermanubis",
            "string": "A 1st century CE marble statue of Hermanubis was found in Baiae, Italy, combining the attributes of the Greek god Hermes and the Egyptian god Anubis, both guides to the souls of the dead. The statue is currently displayed at the National Maritime Museum in Sydney, Australia."
        }
    },
    "thoughts":
    {
        "text": "I discovered a page on ancient.eu with an illustration of a Hermanubis statue from Baiae, Italy, dating back to the 1st century CE.",
        "reasoning": "The information about the statue might provide an interesting perspective on Hermanubis' appearance and how the deity was perceived. This will be a useful addition to the essay.",
        "plan": "- Save the information about the statue\n- Continue the research\n- Start writing the essay",
        "criticism": "The page mainly focuses on an image; however, the information about the statue's origin and features might still be valuable to the essay.",
        "summaryforgpt": "I have browsed five sources about Hermanubis and saved results in googleresults0.txt, websiteresults1.txt, websiteresults2.txt, websiteresults3.txt, websiteresults4.txt, and websiteresults5_statue.txt. I'm currently on the task of writing a 5000-word essay about Hermanubis. The latest source discussed a 1st century CE statue found in Baiae, Italy, portraying the combination of Hermes and Anubis."
    }
}

{
    "command": {
        "name": "start_agent",
        "args":{
            "name": "EssayWriter",
            "task": "Write essay",
            "Commands":[
                "write_to_file",
                "append_to_file",
                "read_file",
                "count_words",
                "memory_retrieve"
            ],
            "prompt": "You are an AI Agent tasked with writing a 5000-word essay about Hermanubis. You can write to, read, and append files. Make use of the information I have stored in my memory from browsing multiple websites (memory_retrieve). Begin by outlining the essay and then start writing it in chunks. Save your progress in a file named Hermanubis.docx."
        }
    },
    "thoughts":
    {
        "text": "I'll start by creating an AI Agent called EssayWriter to handle the task of writing the 5000-word essay on Hermanubis.",
        "reasoning": "By delegating the task to an AI Agent, I can better focus on collecting information and ensuring the essay maintains a consistent structure and coherent perspective.",
        "plan": "- Create the EssayWriter Agent\n- Guide the EssayWriter Agent to outline the essay\n- Write the essay in chunks\n- Save the essay progress to Hermanubis.docx",
        "criticism": "I still need to be vigilant in providing the necessary information and guidance to the EssayWriter Agent to ensure the end result is coherent and well-researched.",
        "summaryforgpt": "So far, I have browsed five sources about Hermanubis and saved results in googleresults0.txt, websiteresults1.txt, websiteresults2.txt, websiteresults3.txt, websiteresults4.txt, and websiteresults5_statue.txt. I'm delegated the task of writing a 5000-word essay about Hermanubis to an AI Agent named EssayWriter. I will guide the Agent through outlining and writing the essay while ensuring adequate information is provided from my memory."
    }
}

{
    "command": {
        "name": "message_agent",
        "args":{
            "name": "EssayWriter",
            "message": "First, outline the essay structure by breaking it into sections such as introduction, cultural significance, historical context, the composite deity, iconography, and conclusion. Then, begin writing the introduction to Hermanubis, providing a brief overview of the deity and the essay's purpose."
        }
    },
    "thoughts":
    {
        "text": "I am providing the EssayWriter with guidance for outlining the essay structure and beginning with the introduction.",
        "reasoning": "By providing this guidance, I can ensure the essay has a logical structure and covers all essential aspects of Hermanubis.",
        "plan": "- Instruct the Agent to create an outline\n- Oversee the Agent while writing the essay\n- Guide the Agent through each section",
        "criticism": "I need to ensure the Agent uses the information I gathered effectively and maintains a coherent and detailed essay.",
        "summaryforgpt": "I have browsed five sources about Hermanubis and saved results in googleresults0.txt, websiteresults1.txt, websiteresults2.txt, websiteresults3.txt, websiteresults4.txt, and websiteresults5_statue.txt. I've started the AI Agent EssayWriter to write the 5000-word essay about Hermanubis. Now, I'm providing guidance for outlining the essay's structure and instructing the Agent to begin writing the introduction."
    }
}

{
    "command": {
        "name": "message_agent",
        "args":{
            "name": "EssayWriter",
            "message": "Continue following the outline you've created for the essay. Write the next sections, focusing on the cultural significance, historical context, the composite deity, and iconography of Hermanubis. Make sure to incorporate information from my memory to provide a comprehensive understanding of the deity. Keep track of the word count, and save your progress to Hermanubis.docx."
        }
    },
    "thoughts":
    {
        "text": "I will guide the EssayWriter to continue following the outline and write the subsequent sections of the essay.",
        "reasoning": "This approach will ensure that all essential aspects of Hermanubis are covered logically and coherently, ultimately producing a well-researched and insightful essay.",
        "plan": "- Instruct the Agent to write the subsequent sections\n- Oversee the Agent's progress\n- Monitor the word count\n- Make sure the Agent saves progress to Hermanubis.docx",
        "criticism": "I should be mindful of the word count while guiding the EssayWriter Agent to ensure that the essay doesn't exceed or fall short of the 5000-word limit.",
        "summaryforgpt": "I have browsed five sources about Hermanubis and saved results in googleresults0.txt, websiteresults1.txt, websiteresults2.txt, websiteresults3.txt, websiteresults4.txt, and websiteresults5_statue.txt. I've started the AI Agent EssayWriter to write the 5000-word essay about Hermanubis. I'm guiding the Agent through outlining the essay structure and instructing the Agent to continue writing the essay, focusing on the cultural significance, historical context, the composite deity, and iconography sections."
    }
}

{
    "command": {
        "name": "message_agent",
        "args":{
            "name": "EssayWriter",
            "message": "Having covered the cultural significance, historical context, the composite deity, and iconography sections, now write the conclusion for the essay. Summarize the main points covered in the essay and provide a final analysis of the deity's impact on the cultures in which it was revered. Ensure that the word count is approximately 5000 words and save the completed essay to Hermanubis.docx."
        }
    },
    "thoughts":
    {
        "text": "I will instruct the EssayWriter to write the conclusion, summarizing the main points and providing a final analysis.",
        "reasoning": "A suitable conclusion will wrap up the essay, providing closure and reinforcing the essential points covered throughout the text.",
        "plan": "- Instruct the Agent to write the conclusion\n- Monitor word count\n- Make sure the Agent saves the final essay to Hermanubis.docx",
        "criticism": "It's important to ensure that the conclusion doesn't introduce any new concepts and maintains a coherent analysis in line with the rest of the essay.",
        "summaryforgpt": "I have browsed five sources about Hermanubis and saved results in googleresults0.txt, websiteresults1.txt, websiteresults2.txt, websiteresults3.txt, websiteresults4.txt, and websiteresults5_statue.txt. I've started the AI Agent EssayWriter to write the 5000-word essay about Hermanubis. I'm now instructing the Agent to write the conclusion of the essay, summarizing the main points and providing final analysis, while ensuring the word count is approximately 5000 words."
